            "name": "/u/avi@chromium.org/", 
            "email": "/u/avi@chromium.org/"
        }, 
        {
            "date": "2010-02-22 10:34:18", 
            "sentences": [
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "I would love to get rid of classic, but we need some way to force a return to default theme from the themes \ngallery.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "I think the correct answer is probably something on the page that isn't a part of the gallery -- because \nthe default themes are different across platforms (and even between Aero and \"Classic\" on Win, for example), any \ngallery image will be misleading.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "Maybe a button at the top to \"Reset to default\" with an theme that specifically \ntriggers the default theme reload (as opposed to having no images).", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }
            ], 
            "name": "/u/@UBBTS1xSARBHVwR8EQ%3D%3D/", 
            "email": "/u/@UBBTS1xSARBHVwR8EQ%3D%3D/"
        }, 
        {
            "date": "2010-02-22 14:37:27", 
            "sentences": [
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "I don't think users would be confused by side-by-side thumbnails of \"Default Theme\" and \"Classic Theme\" in the \nthemes gallery.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "It's certainly easier to discover (and less ambiguous) than the current solution - \"Preferences\" / \n\"Personal Stuff\" tab / \"Reset to default theme\" button.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }
            ], 
            "name": "/u/@VxNeQFNWBRRDXAN7/", 
